1.4.name: wordpress/fightback-plugin
1.4.description:
This plugin is a part of the FightBackNetworks System http://fightbacknetwork.com - it allows you to register your blog in it and then receive the posts from the the system.

To register your blog must meet the several requirements:

  • your blog must be located in the root of web server
  • subdomains and IPs are not allowed
  • standart WP theme is not allowed
  • no standart post "Hello World!" & page "Sample Page" on blog
  • Google analytics and adsense must be disabled
  • your blog must not be banned by google
  • WP MultiUser is not available

The available posting settings:

  • specify the post categories to post into
  • specify the post authors
